Zero to App: Develop with Firebase

https://events.google.com/io2016/schedule?sid=c8641ff7-0bef-e511-a517-00155d5066d7#day3/c8641ff7-0bef-e511-a517-00155d5066d7

1. Firebase Scales automatically
2. JSON tree data structure in DB
3. Chat App
4. Database connect - No network check, no background thread, no polling etc.
5. Disconnection handled seamlesslessly, no extra coding require
6. Authentication - easy sign in
7. Session - No need to login every time, but if phone lost, protect data
8. Password reset flow - UI as well in your own domain
9. Anonymous accounts - attach credentials to existing record eg. add to cart and then sign in
10. Storage - upload/download, Auto scale, Vision API, user access    
11. Docs, dev tools (android studio integration), support (free and paid)
